title: Coffee Urns - Trip Handle Maintenance/Replacement
description:
Watch this short video to find out how to remove the trip handle from your coffee urn from Hamilton Beach Commercial in order to maintain or replace it. These instructions apply for the following models:

→ Brewstation® 110 Cup Coffee Urn - HCU110S
→ Brewstation® 65 Cup Coffee Urn - HCU065S
→ Brewstation® 45 Cup Coffee Urn - HCU045S
→ 60 Cup Coffee Urn - D50065

For more product information, visit: http://bit.ly/Coffee-Urns
